data.text:
Welcome to my personal notes wiki. This is where I keep notes on everything I learn.

Please feel free to browse. I generally use search, but you can navigate to most places from this homepage.

I've had these notes for a very long time, I make no guarantees that they are accurate, or complete (updated as used).
